<ab><lb n="1"/>  <gap reason="lost" unit="character" extent="unknown"/><w lemma="καί">καὶ</w>  <persName type="attested"><name nymRef="#Μελίτιος">Μελίτιον</name>  <persName type="attested"><name nymRef="#Πυθίων">Πυθίω<milestone unit="block"/>νος</name></persName></persName>  <lb n="2"/><gap reason="lost" unit="character" extent="unknown"/><orig n="unresolved">ν</orig>  <w lemma="καί">καὶ</w>  <w lemma="ὁ">τ<gap reason="lost" unit="character" id="gap04" quantity="1"/><certainty target="gap04" locus="#gi" degree="low" assertedValue="space"/>ὰ</w>  <w lemma="ἐν">ἐν</w>  <w lemma="αὐτός">αὐτοῖς</w>  <milestone unit="block"/>    <w lemma="πᾶς">πάντα</w> <lb n="3"/><gap reason="lost" unit="character" extent="unknown"/>  <w lemma="ἐκ"><supplied reason="lost">ἐκ</supplied></w>  <w lemma="ὁ"><supplied reason="lost">τ</supplied>ῶν</w>  <w lemma="ἴδιος">ἰδίων</w>  <gap reason="lost" unit="character" quantity="2"/><space extent="7" unit="character" dim="horizontal"/><milestone unit="block"/> <space extent="1" unit="line" dim="horizontal"/></ab>
</div>
         <div type="apparatus">
            <p>l. 2,  apparently a fault in the stone between <foreign xml:lang="grc">Τ</foreign> and <foreign xml:lang="grc">Α</foreign>.</p>
         </div>
         <div type="translation">
            <p>
               <gap reason="lost" unit="character" extent="unknown"/> and Melition daughter of Pythion made the <gap reason="lost" unit="character" extent="unknown"/> and everything in them   <gap reason="lost" unit="character" extent="unknown"/>
               <supplied reason="lost">at</supplied> their own expense <gap reason="lost" unit="character" extent="unknown"/>
            </p>
         </div>
         <div type="commentary" n="none">
            <p>
There is insufficient evidence to show what was built but it should be noted that it is described by a plural pronoun. The builders are likely to have been a man (name lost) and his wife who is not at present identifiable.</p>
         </div>
